name: Parrot
description: Macaws are a group of 17 species of spectacularly colorful parrots from South and Central America and Mexico. They are known for their great intelligence and playfulness. Macaws are long-lived, and often kept as pets. The Jubilee Macaw is a cross between a Harlequin Macaw and a Green-winged Macaw.*An acrylic stand is included for display purposes.
